data.name: richTextBox1.Text
data.value:
This tool is created by Velorexe. It converts the Veekun Database to the Pokemon Unity PokemonDatabase.cs format. The most important thing to have is the entire CSV format of Veekun's Database (which is provided with the GitHub version of this tool).
The 'Source Folder' will open a File Explorer Window which will allow you to select the folder with the CSV files of Veekun's Database The 'Output Folder' does the same as 'Source Folder', but it'll allow you to select folder for the output file (wich will be in a .txt format) When you hit 'Export' the tool will go through every single Pokemon entry (to the generation that you picked).
The example format shows Bulbasaur as an example. It's a shortened version of the final output. It only shows which PKUnity PokemonData version it's on.
